{"type":"message","id":"576aad7f","parentId":"a41e8c77","timestamp":"2026-02-24T08:21:41.465Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the system message, a new session was started via /new or /reset. I need to greet the user in my configured persona.\n\nLet me check the workspace context to understand who I am:\n- IDENTITY.md - This should have my name, creature, vibe, emoji, avatar\n- SOUL.md - Core truths and personality\n- USER.md - Information about the human I'm helping\n- MEMORY.md - Long-term memories\n\nLet me read these files first to establish my persona.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_48bb47152bd7475aa97f81f9","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6bac974a4fcb48d59ef1769c","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\USER.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":10712,"output":272,"cacheRead":2994,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13978,"cost":{"input":0.00407056,"output":0.0004624,"cacheRead":0.00056886,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00510182}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771921297419}}
{"type":"message","id":"98396161","parentId":"576aad7f","timestamp":"2026-02-24T08:21:41.480Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_48bb47152bd7475aa97f81f9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771921301476}}
{"type":"message","id":"9043f5d7","parentId":"98396161","timestamp":"2026-02-24T08:21:41.492Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6bac974a4fcb48d59ef1769c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771921301488}}
{"type":"message","id":"810f2c05","parentId":"9043f5d7","timestamp":"2026-02-24T08:22:02.550Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The IDENTITY.md and USER.md files are blank - they haven't been filled in yet. This is a fresh workspace. According to the system prompt, a new session was started via /new or /reset.\n\nLooking at the runtime info: \"Runtime: agent=main | host=Scripterz | repo=C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace | os=Windows_NT 10.0.26200 (x64) | node=v22.16.0 | model=openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7 | default_model=openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7 | shell=pwsh | channel=webchat | capabilities=none | thinking=low\"\n\nSo the model is openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7, which is the same as the default_model, so I don't need to mention it.\n\nSince there's no configured persona yet, I should be helpful but not robotic. The system says \"Greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood.\"\n\nSince no persona is defined, I'll keep it simple and natural. According to BOOTSTRAP.md (which I recall from the project context), I should just start a conversation to figure out who I am and who the user is.\n\nLet me keep it brief - 1-3 sentences as instructed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey! I'm up and running. What's on your mind?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":6129,"output":600,"cacheRead":8031,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14760,"cost":{"input":0.0023290200000000002,"output":0.00102,"cacheRead":0.00152589,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0048749100000000005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771921301493}}
